@node Options "Editor Options"

  Name          HotKey    Description
  -----------------------------------
  # Lines       L         Number of couloured lines.
  Speed         E         Speed of blanker module.
  Hor. Mirror   H         Mirror across the horizontal axis.
  Ver. Mirror   V         Mirror across the vertical axis.

  Screen Mode   M         Selects display mode.

  Save          S         Saves preferences.
  Cancel        C         Exit/Cancel without saving.
  Priority      P         Only change if you are experienced with AmigaDOS!

  Music         .         Music module file requester.

@endnode
